item.title: CVE-2022-2593|2024-08-03T00:39:07.994Z -- unknown -- better%20search%20replace
item.description: The Better Search Replace WordPress plugin before 1.4.1 does not properly sanitise and escape table data before inserting it into a SQL query, which could allow high privilege users to perform SQL Injection attacks
